			<h1 class="title">About manifoldJS</h1>
			<p>manifoldJS is the easy, fast way to wrap your website into native "hosted" apps for every platform. You can use the generator or include the NPM package in your existing build tools to quickly generate container apps that are ready to be deployed to the Windows Store, App Store and Google Play Store.</p>
		</div>

		<h3>Who created manifoldJS</h3>
		<p class="slim">manifoldJS is an open source project built by a small group of passionate engineers and technical evangelists at Microsoft. Special thanks to the <a href="http://www.w3.org/2008/webapps/" target="_blank">W3C App Manifest working group</a> and <a href="https://cordova.apache.org/" target="_blank">Apache Cordova team</a> for helping make manifoldJS possible.</p>
		<p>Help us improve manifoldJS @ <a href="https://github.com/manifoldjs">github.com/manifoldjs</a>.</p>

